title: Etsy : global gross merchandise volume Q4 2019
summary: The Etsy global Quarter in the merchandise volume was Quarter Q2_'19 , who made 1655.72 million .
The most global Quarter was Q4_'18 , with just 719.04 million .

In second place was Quarter Q3_'19 with 1200.37 million ; third place went to Quarter Q4_'19 with 1655.72 million ; fourth place went to Quarter Q1_'17 with 719.04 million and fifth place went to Quarter Q1_'19 , who was 1024.03 million .
gold: This statistic shows the global gross merchandise sales of Etsy Inc. as of the fourth quarter of 2019 . During that period , the C2C e-commerce company generated GMS of 1.66 billion U.S. dollars , up from 1.25 billion U.S. dollars in the corresponding quarter of the previous year . This represents a 32.8 percent year-on-year growth .
